Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.47,0:00:06.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.62,0:00:07.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.30,0:00:12.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的純真還真不像是個殺手啊 塔茲米
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.14,0:00:14.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是個有趣的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.63,0:00:18.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐這個比想像還有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.48,0:00:18.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是很好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.00,0:00:24.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一點也不好
